{"tid":1709973,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔仔吃西瓜 !","createTime":"2019-11-12T04:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T00:03:30.000Z","uid":197098,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96800305af3135e8255614fa9e54d735bfde7548","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"由於糖份高，這video分咗幾日比兔仔食。糖份高不宜多吃，否則損害腸胃，患上致命的GI stasis!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSXw7zGeWMhU&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d18e9be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SXw7zGeWMhU</a>"},{"pid":"bc1b7d3d8d96d88ec1ad7b925f3710c95ceef73e","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T07:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3c8e68d04e40563eb186af5597ac8bb92e0cc65","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T14:41:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有些人會問: 為什麼我在東, 牠會面向著西?</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其實兔子<strong><ins>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</ins></strong>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<strong><ins>你在牠後面也會看到你</ins></strong>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<br />\n兔子🐰是親人的群體性動物，但身體語言與其他動物不同，要做些研究才理解。(推介最底的3個網站)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親人的動物：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMaovq8Vz1LM&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=40e62cb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Maovq8Vz1LM</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpyL0yEs-ka8&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=1f6ad93e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pyL0yEs-ka8</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子的行為解釋網站：</span><br />\n<br />\n香港兔協:&nbsp;<a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2Fknowledge8_ch.php&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=95bdc19d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/knowledge8_ch.php</a><br />\n<br />\n美國兔協 House Rabbit Society (教育網站):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbit.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=981345e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbit.org</a><br />\n<br />\n詳盡身體語言解釋(喜怒哀樂):&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=4040fb50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>"},{"pid":"bf4bbcbf909877737179f33cdada264bca98f162","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T05:46:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子是應該要被絕育</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"c251b8b93687a531d039a518ef7e0693a2125488","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T12:02:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子會不會叫? 是會的....</span></span><br />\n<br />\n開心時會「<span style=\"color: red;\">屋屋</span>」聲叫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmPoSiZmzo58&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=9a5294cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mPoSiZmzo58</a><br />\n<br />\n不滿時會<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。後腳大力踏地代表不滿，但也可以代表驚慌覺得有危險，要看當時的情況。在大自然內，兔子後腳大力踏地是用來警告其他兔仔(包括你)有危險。當兔子遇到巨大驚慌或痛苦也會尖叫，例如被捕獵者(predator)追殺和吃的時候，當然這情況是很慘。<br />\n<br />\n以下video 可看到<span style=\"color: red;\">咕咕叫</span>。當牠用鼻碰主人的手然後縮低代表想被撫摸:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ8wfR7k3844&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=f62431e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z8wfR7k3844</a>"},{"pid":"8c5eaed73a8254bc584e476ea45d705b3ad0baa2","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:07:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人! ☺</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是一種好心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是牠的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=73e5a7a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a>"},{"pid":"bbd4feca7d6c2a8651f9b135f5aa74f144ac6e71","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:05:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子開心到極!&nbsp;🌟🐰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活。兔子也會舒適地躺在地上，伸展手腳，還會打翻騰。室內飼養會比室外養長命，因為沒有天氣和敵人威脅，感到安全、平靜和舒適。狗吠聲、雷暴、消防車叫聲等也會嚇驚兔子。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom(撫摸/親吻)牠們，令牠們冷靜下來知道是沒事的。我家的兔子一聽到吸塵機聲音就嚇驚，所以每次我工人吸塵的時候，我會一直撫摸他們，幾次後他們已習慣了 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=287c1b06\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DE90ikFGQTqs&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d5f23586\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=E90ikFGQTqs</a>"},{"pid":"ececa126b360d458a4f232b6dc8e2525c5bbc676","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:48:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子同屋企小朋友玩耍, 是人類的朋友 !</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAyUYeLrXqug&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=1d8bf49e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AyUYeLrXqug</a>"},{"pid":"bdc2817c90de957c55555460d585c43799c6fafe","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子的睡窩被貓霸佔了 !</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子是被捕獵的動物(prey animal)，在大自然內是每個捕獵者(predator)的目標，沒有自然本能去攻擊他人，牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2HMWjTXFwuY&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=1148388d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2HMWjTXFwuY</a>"},{"pid":"5ae452150fafbb8e84d7a939bdcbba7a32cd8163","tid":1709973,"uid":276382,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T04:04:16.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6843c60f38c94200f3eb95ca6e56e528269f591d","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兔子不滿吃飯時被拍攝，上前搞灣2部攝錄機</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlE5Qexr-jos&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=c537f55b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lE5Qexr-jos</a>"},{"pid":"774ed381db50e9fb848268416e698bc17b5e7555","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T10:52:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">識入樽的兔仔破世界健力士紀錄 !</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXNJmeXb4Y0A&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=a41d97f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XNJmeXb4Y0A</a>"},{"pid":"c53823010d38e2e9161b87160550574ba4dfec45","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢同主人玩：</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs-7b9X5x_Ro&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=44855a47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s-7b9X5x_Ro</a>"},{"pid":"37da8450f55aa4cc85b681a1ec1effae685b691a","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:20:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">兔子發夢飲水:</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkoTWmdwLlp8&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=551cc418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/koTWmdwLlp8</a>"},{"pid":"0e759ef07da7d3138bc99919a73216f85b2b6229","tid":1709973,"uid":208702,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<br />\n功效：滋陰涼血，益氣潤膚，解毒祛熱"},{"pid":"70c10f828a70a8c15ed8663473d330ba8deab9b9","tid":1709973,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:57.000Z","msg":"打緊仗仲講免"},{"pid":"fd3f9584646cab59d201420f5ccf9ce010617df4","tid":1709973,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:12:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">領養了兔子,瘋狂跳兔子舞!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n跳兔子舞(Binky)是兔子最開心的狀態。這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMu27kYckovg&d=4awEA7knrPrnmlrQXGUFYmLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=d9b5f95f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Mu27kYckovg</a>"},{"pid":"be04ba605ee1dd86b5117e72d4558b9e697c13c4","tid":1709973,"uid":117843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"好可愛嘅兔兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62df4e1c6b6ddf41968883b813336be22a67e713","tid":1709973,"uid":306000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e759ef07da7d3138bc99919a73216f85b2b6229","tid":1709973,"uid":208702,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"淮杞兔肉湯<br />\n<br />\n原料：兔肉、淮山藥、枸杞、桂圓、鹽、雞精、料酒、姜。<br />\n<br />\n製法：將兔肉洗凈切成塊；姜切片，山藥切塊待用；坐鍋點火倒入水，放入兔肉、薑片、桂圓、山藥，加入料酒、雞精調味，燉1小時；將枸杞用溫水泡好，開蓋後，加入枸杞改小火再燉半小時，關火後加鹽調味即可食用。<br />\n<br />\n用法：食肉喝湯。<br />\n<